{"tid":1560631,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車然係咁：障礙處處的瑞和街","createTime":"2019-09-11T09:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:12:23.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59bdf01e292225d0bb2f30e14c4deb0092067e2f","tid":1560631,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190906/photo/bkn-20190906190017129-0906_00982_001_01p.jpg?20190906190400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190906190017129-0906_00982_001_01p.jpg%3F20190906190400&h=7bd3472a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條街對於觀塘區街坊而言無人不識，因為長期被兩旁商舖放滿雜物在馬路上，駕駛者經過時經常被「菜蘿」和「發泡膠箱」阻礙，道路本來的上落客貨區亦被車長期佔用，地上更滿是積水，衞生情況欠佳，不少街坊稱已向相關部門投訴，但有沒有改善？大家有眼睇，奉勸駕駛人士如無必要都不要駛進這條路障處處的瑞和街為妙。"},{"pid":"4ae181613feb38dbd9659ff4dec3bf53e3caa151","tid":1560631,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"本地豬農：叉燒飯藏針相信源於為豬隻打針時用到的針咀被弄斷<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1130385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1130385</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街掃違例泊車 揭運魚車司機停牌駕駛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1186592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1186592</a><br />\n<br />\n港府滅鼠落後 瑞和街市鼠患嚴重<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bLDCvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bLDCvS</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街水果店雪櫃短路起火 逾百居民疏散<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1150423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1150423</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街發泡膠山圍城 空談回收政府袖手 <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1091557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1091557</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街後巷雜物遭縱火 警追緝縱火狂徒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cpqqsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cpqqsS</a><br />\n<br />\n​「新界仔優質果菜」觀塘瑞和街分店持續播放叫賣錄音造成噪音煩擾被定罪<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/866940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/866940</a><br />\n<br />\n[全港最平] 瑞和街 橙售價為12元3個、菜心每斤9元，而生菜為5元一斤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/912860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/912860</a>"},{"pid":"f71c50577ce7e91d37d0a5d42f355617b350030d","tid":1560631,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"46e3b1cea70f9c348c1fc7f615c4535ec103539f","tid":1560631,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f71c50577ce7e91d37d0a5d42f355617b350030d","tid":1560631,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"